Creating an image of a drive:
  dd if=<driveLocation> of=<pathToImage/imageName.img> bs=1M count=<sizeOf.imgInBytes>

  where:
	  bs is how many bytes to write at a time.
	  Count is how many megabytes
	  if is the drive to create an image of (typically uses /dev/<sdb/sda/sdc/etc)
	  of is the name of the image.
